Pictured above: Puttu Fry with ... more Image 30 of 30 Houston's top Asian restaurants of 2015 1 / 30 Back to Gallery The Far East has a seat at the table in Houston's eclectic foodie scene. And when it comes to the best flavors in town, we handpicked some of our favorites we think you should try.
Every year, Houston Chronicle food critic Alison Cook selects her top 100 restaurants of 2015. From there, we divided out the restaurants by cuisine type.
RELATED: Houston's top 100 restaurants of 2015
Asian cuisine on this list includes Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Malaysian, Indonesian, Thai, Vietnamese, Persian and Indian restaurants.
Take a look at the gallery above for Houston's best Asian restaurants of 2015.
